#lg B	cagbatuku


@(4-9=c2553.B.4) -- head high, surpassing everyone, breed-bull, who makes the seeds sprout, whose name is respected, spreading great terror, whose august commands cannot be countermanded, who is imbued with awesomeness on the mountain of pure divine powers, who has taken his seat on the great throne-dais, @wDN{An}, the king of the gods --

#trailer rubric	cagbatuku


@(10=c2553.B.10) @fsux{šagbatuku}.

#lg C	cagbatuku


@(11-18=c2553.C.11) -- has looked at him with long-lasting favour, has looked at prince @wRN{Lipit-@wDN{Eštar}} with favour. He has bestowed on him a long life, he has bestowed on prince @wRN{Lipit-@wDN{Eštar}} a long life. The words of what @wDN{An} says are firmly established; no god would oppose them. At the place where the destinies are to be decided, all the @wDN{Anuna} gods gather around him.

#trailer rubric	cagbatuku


@(19=c2553.C.19) @fsux{šagbatuku}.

